# Overview

<!-- badges: start -->

<!-- badges: end -->

A repository of supplementary materials for an undergraduate thesis project by Andie Prasetyo ([Bachelor of English Literature](https://sasing.unud.ac.id/) [BoEL] program, Faculty of Humanities, Udayana University). The topic is on English negative prefixes in the *Wrecker* novel.
